**** DEPENDENCIES ****

- The [bin] section of the configuration file contains various programs required
  by the testing framework.

- You should install some Python libraries:

  - Python Imaging Library (PIL).
    http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/

  - Python Crontab
    http://pypi.python.org/pypi/python-crontab/

  - Python PLY
    http://www.dabeaz.com/ply/

  - Selenium Python Driver
    http://pypi.python.org/pypi/selenium/

  See http://docs.python.org/install/index.html for how to install them.

- To generate the doxygen documentation, you need some filters:

  - Doxygen filter for Python:
    http://pypi.python.org/pypi/doxypy/

  - Doxygen filter for Perl:
    http://www.bigsister.ch/doxygenfilter/

  - Doxygen filter for Javascript:
    http://svn.berlios.de/wsvn/jsunit/trunk/jsunit/util/js2doxy.pl

**** INTALLATION ****

1) cp default.cfg custom.cfg
2) edit custom.cfg to parameter the testing framework
3) make config
4) make doc
5) make runServer
